{"id": "ChIJWSN5pYzDwoARyg0Qdw6Sfkg", "rating": 4.6, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_MODERATE", "userRatingCount": 634, "displayName": {"text": "Mendocino Farms", "languageCode": "en"}, "editorialSummary": {"text": "Creative gourmet sandwiches, soups & salads, made with local & seasonal ingredients.", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJWSN5pYzDwoARyg0Qdw6Sfkg/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pkQlpFeFBZWEJYTldaRmFVNXllbFkzYTNSUlVrRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Try this place for their delicious, healthy and interesting sandwiches, wraps and more. Prices were reasonable. Service was friendly, quick, portions were generous and the place was clean and roomie. Try the outdoor eating area and watch the world pass by on Lake Avenue.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Try this place for their delicious, healthy and interesting sandwiches, wraps and more. Prices were reasonable. Service was friendly, quick, portions were generous and the place was clean and roomie. Try the outdoor eating area and watch the world pass by on Lake Avenue.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Citygal", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/113632644292482428215/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocId6qedaDkaCPwJBFj3dwffOjVY2iCFiCTZcHLervfwyL-P9A=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-13T19:34:41.841735663Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pkQlpFeFBZWEJYTldaRmFVNXllbFkzYTNSUlVrRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pkQlpFeFBZWEJYTldaRmFVNXllbFkzYTNSUlVrRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c38ca5792359:0x487e920e77100dca"}, {"name": "places/ChIJWSN5pYzDwoARyg0Qdw6Sfkg/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2w5RVEyOXFhbUZRWVdrMU1FczRabEJRUlZOaGRXYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 weeks ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "awesome lunch spot! had the modern Caesar and tomato 🍅 basil soup. Heavenly!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "awesome lunch spot! had the modern Caesar and tomato 🍅 basil soup. Heavenly!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Cooper Klinger", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110704458704597404721/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWVD83DZCi6DDS3BVvK09xH4F26X8JeyvIkOvI45M1Jl3_QmRHCjQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-16T20:31:29.298027937Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2w5RVEyOXFhbUZRWVdrMU1FczRabEJRUlZOaGRXYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2w5RVEyOXFhbUZRWVdrMU1FczRabEJRUlZOaGRXYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c38ca5792359:0x487e920e77100dca"}, {"name": "places/ChIJWSN5pYzDwoARyg0Qdw6Sfkg/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnTURBNE52b0JREAE", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a year ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I heard from my coworkers at work that their salads and sandwiches were the best in town, so I decided to order and see what it’s all about. Let me tell you, one of the best sandwiches and salad I’ve had in years! I was new to the place, so I was a little lost until I was created by Billy. One of the best experiences I’ve had. That guy loves what he does, very passionate individual. He took his time and recommended me to try out the Farm club and the Thai Mango salad. The sandwich had so much flavor, I think it was the delicious pickled onions and let me tell ya, it had a great amount of turkey. I love some avocado on my sandwiches and this sandwich came with it. The salad was one of the best salads I’ve had. I will forever remember it. I’m no longer a Panera guy and I’m officially a Mendocino guy forever now! You guys have someone good please and make sure Billy stays forever at this location. I will personally make the long drive just for that guy and rest of his team. Thanks again, Billy\n\nYou’re the man! :)", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I heard from my coworkers at work that their salads and sandwiches were the best in town, so I decided to order and see what it’s all about. Let me tell you, one of the best sandwiches and salad I’ve had in years! I was new to the place, so I was a little lost until I was created by Billy. One of the best experiences I’ve had. That guy loves what he does, very passionate individual. He took his time and recommended me to try out the Farm club and the Thai Mango salad. The sandwich had so much flavor, I think it was the delicious pickled onions and let me tell ya, it had a great amount of turkey. I love some avocado on my sandwiches and this sandwich came with it. The salad was one of the best salads I’ve had. I will forever remember it. I’m no longer a Panera guy and I’m officially a Mendocino guy forever now! You guys have someone good please and make sure Billy stays forever at this location. I will personally make the long drive just for that guy and rest of his team. Thanks again, Billy\n\nYou’re the man! :)", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "John Castaneda", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102021148531868939665/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI0qzPiZHNDDm6cKxZrVFbE3bs4qWtF0b-30NIANgVBvEKk1g=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2025-02-06T06:10:16.534856Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnTURBNE52b0JREAE&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnTURBNE52b0JREAE!2m1!1s0x80c2c38ca5792359:0x487e920e77100dca"}, {"name": "places/ChIJWSN5pYzDwoARyg0Qdw6Sfkg/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNMa0szNzJnRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a year ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I heard their salads and sandwiches were famous, so I made the trip. Parking was busy during the lunch rush but worth the trip.\n\nI had the Chinese chicken salad.  Probably one of my favorite iterations for this salad I’ve ever had. It tasted very fresh, the cashews were delicious, the chicken quality was excellent and the dressing was perfect. Overall it made for an amazing salad.\n\nI’d definitely come back here again to try their other items or just get the same salad again. During peak times, parking can be really really busy.\n\n***update***\nDined in and it was a very spacious spot and customer service was excellent. I tried their Caesar with quinoa and it was delicious. Their fried chicken is pretty good and their cookies are worth a try.\n\nTheir corn chowder is delicious along with their Bahn mi pork belly. Two excellent menu items to pair together.  The black tie turkey sandwich was also excellent and I highly recommend it.\n\nThe Thai mango chicken salad is phenomenal and is my favorite dish they got so far. Overall an excellent and filling lunch option.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I heard their salads and sandwiches were famous, so I made the trip. Parking was busy during the lunch rush but worth the trip.\n\nI had the Chinese chicken salad.  Probably one of my favorite iterations for this salad I’ve ever had. It tasted very fresh, the cashews were delicious, the chicken quality was excellent and the dressing was perfect. Overall it made for an amazing salad.\n\nI’d definitely come back here again to try their other items or just get the same salad again. During peak times, parking can be really really busy.\n\n***update***\nDined in and it was a very spacious spot and customer service was excellent. I tried their Caesar with quinoa and it was delicious. Their fried chicken is pretty good and their cookies are worth a try.\n\nTheir corn chowder is delicious along with their Bahn mi pork belly. Two excellent menu items to pair together.  The black tie turkey sandwich was also excellent and I highly recommend it.\n\nThe Thai mango chicken salad is phenomenal and is my favorite dish they got so far. Overall an excellent and filling lunch option.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "funning", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110827233308643416287/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV8eBl2cEQrW_I0wLzkTGJfbzU3l3DVtdSN1SSpmiH9IiBxJ8s=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba7"}, "publishTime": "2024-10-17T22:35:25.713451Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNMa0szNzJnRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNMa0szNzJnRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c38ca5792359:0x487e920e77100dca"}, {"name": "places/ChIJWSN5pYzDwoARyg0Qdw6Sfkg/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25WWFUwdGFaRUZhWTIxRWFFUlJNVVUzYkUxTlJFRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I had a truly wonderful experience at this restaurant. The food came out fresher than any other Mendocino farms I have been to. The environment was buzzing at lunchtime and the food was out quickly. Made my day better and I’ll definitely be going back for lunch soon. The turkey avo Sandwich did Not disappoint", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I had a truly wonderful experience at this restaurant. The food came out fresher than any other Mendocino farms I have been to. The environment was buzzing at lunchtime and the food was out quickly. Made my day better and I’ll definitely be going back for lunch soon. The turkey avo Sandwich did Not disappoint", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Tommy Hays", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100917436062807353793/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWvBsXEu4P-bfmHuTD6KO_LIxQiuHwzhCx1xLrTeskO9CnOWqk4=s128-c0x0000000